279
00:17:02,017 --> 00:17:03,302
Chocolate chip.

280
00:17:03,315 --> 00:17:04,653
Cookies!

281
00:17:04,705 --> 00:17:05,923
Homemade.

282
00:17:05,965 --> 00:17:07,560
