You know, the blood thing.

297
00:17:47,735 --> 00:17:51,900
And then a crime scene
and more blood.

298
00:17:52,368 --> 00:17:54,401
I don't know how you do it.

299
00:17:54,435 --> 00:17:55,462
Well, blood is...

300
00:17:55,605 --> 00:17:56,831
<i>...my life.

301
00:17:56,936 --> 00:17:58,203
...my job.

302
00:17:58,237 --> 00:18:00,900
<i>Lately, the thing that
surprises me most about Rita

303
00:18:00,925 --> 00:18:02,640
<i>is how much I like being with her.

304
00:18:02,677 --> 00:18:04,881
<i>But whenever that happens
with a woman,

305
00:18:04,898 --> 00:18:08,233
<i>when I feel comfortable with
her, it all goes wrong.

306
00:18:08,976 --> 00:18:12,030
<i>That's why I think it's best
to take it one step at a time.

307
00:18:12,065 --> 00:18:15,603
Hey, you know,
Deb has been all over me

308
00:18:15,636 --> 00:18:17,861
