Make a date.

312
00:18:26,085 --> 00:18:28,363
I pick you.

313
00:18:29,866 --> 00:18:32,833
<i>And I pick my sister to chaperon.

314
00:19:01,937 --> 00:19:03,601
Sister.

315
00:19:03,636 --> 00:19:06,133
So, Miami's the haystack,

316
00:19:06,157 --> 00:19:08,282
